---
---

<div id="inbelt">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="section-label">03 — Inbelt Tech</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Suporte técnico<br>de verdade.</h2>
    <p class="inbelt-sub">
      A Inbelt Tech nasceu da vontade de oferecer um atendimento
      honesto e eficiente. Formatação, manutenção, upgrade de hardware
      — resolvemos com agilidade e sem enrolação.
    </p>
    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service-item">
        <div class="service-icon">🖥️</div>
        <div class="service-name">Formatação</div>
        <div class="service-desc">Windows, drivers e configuração completa do sistema.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-item">
        <div class="service-icon">🔧</div>
        <div class="service-name">Manutenção</div>
        <div class="service-desc">Diagnóstico e reparo de hardware e software.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-item">
        <div class="service-icon">⚡</div>
        <div class="service-name">Upgrade</div>
        <div class="service-desc">Troca de SSD, RAM e componentes pra turbinar seu PC.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-item">
        <div class="service-icon">📝</div>
        <div class="service-name">Consultoria</div>
        <div class="service-desc">Ajudamos na escolha de PCs e notebooks, que mais se encaixam a você.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="inbelt-ctas">
      <a href="https://wa.me/+5512988033200" class="btn-accent">Chamar no WhatsApp</a>
      <a href="https://instagram.com/inbelttech" class="btn-outline">Ver Instagram</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  #inbelt {
    background: #1A1F2E;
    color: #F5F7FA;
    padding: 6rem 3rem;
  }
  .inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .section-label {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: #6ECFCA;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #F5F7FA;
  }
  .inbelt-sub {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: #7A8BA6;
    max-width: 500px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }
  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 1px;
    background: #2a3044;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }
  .service-item {
    background: #1A1F2E;
    padding: 1.8rem 1.5rem;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .service-item:hover { background: #222840; }
  .service-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  .service-name {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    color: #F5F7FA;
  }
  .service-desc {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: #7A8BA6;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .inbelt-ctas { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn-accent {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.6rem;
    background: #6ECFCA;
    color: #1A1F2E;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-accent:hover { background: #4fb8b3; }
  .btn-outline {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.6rem;
    border: 1.5px solid #2a3044;
    color: #7A8BA6;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-outline:hover { border-color: #F5F7FA; color: #F5F7FA; }
</style>